Move Symbol

Select the symbol and drag it to its new position.

Or,

On the Home tab, select Arrow Keys Nudge. Use the arrow keys to move the symbol to its new position.

Move symbols with precision

Right click on the symbol. The Symbol Information dialog box will open.

Change the X-Position and At depth to place the symbol. Note. the symbol will have a reference point (REF1) which will be used for the placement of that symbol.

Click Update and Exit.
